Interface GenericDome

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VirtualDome

    public interface GenericDome
    An interface for the commands that should be available to all domes.
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)

      • isSync

        boolean isSync(LocationElement locHz)
        Returns if the dome is currently synchronized with a given azimuth direction.
        Parameters:
        locHz - The horizontal position of the telescope.
        Returns:
        True if the azimuth direction is visible through the dome's aperture, otherwise false.

      • getSyncTime

      • getFitsHeader

        ImageHeaderElement[] getFitsHeader()
        Returns the fits header describing the status of this dome. The set of entries are: 
         Entry        Value (typical)   Description
 ------------------------------------------
 
 DOM_AZ      10.1              Dome azimuth (deg)             
 DOM_OPEN    true              Dome open ?
 DOM_MOVI    false             Dome moving ?
 DOM_MODE    VIRTUAL           Dome model (driver)
        Returns:
        The set of entries for the fits header.
